    {
      "title": "🦀 Claude Code",
      "url": "https://pages.github.tools.sap/hAIperspace/hai-docs/llm-proxy/recipes/claude/",
      "category": "Tools",
      "notes": "<p><strong>SAP Setup</strong></p><p>hai configure claude-code</p><p>hai proxy start</p><p><br></p><p>SAP Doc</p><p><span style=\"color: black;\">Dear colleagues,</span></p><p><span style=\"color: black;\">Thank you for joining our&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: black;\">high-energy&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"color: black;\">rollout kick-off for Claude Code</span>!</p><p><span style=\"color: black;\">Here are links to the kick-off&nbsp;​</span><a href=\"https://sap.sharepoint.com/:b:/r/teams/ClaudeCodeRollout/Shared%20Documents/General/Resources/20260310_Claude%20Code_Kick-Off%20Roll-Out.pdf?csf=1&amp;web=1&amp;e=bmcOKb\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: rgb(243, 242, 241); color: blue;\"><img src=\"//:0\" alt=\"​pdf icon\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\">&nbsp;slides</a><span style=\"color: black;\">​&nbsp;and&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://video.sap.com/media/t/1_tbpy7x1a\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(150, 96, 125);\">recording</a><span style=\"color: black;\">.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: black;\">Here are the&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: black;\">next steps</strong><span style=\"color: black;\">&nbsp;for you.</span></p><p><br></p><p>1.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pages.github.tools.sap/hAIperspace/hai-docs/llm-proxy/recipes/claude/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(91, 95, 199);\"><u>​</u></a><a href=\"https://pages.github.tools.sap/hAIperspace/hai-docs/llm-proxy/recipes/claude/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(150, 96, 125);\">Set-up</a><span style=\"color: black;\">&nbsp;Claude Code.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: black;\">2. Visit the&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://portal.hyperspace.tools.sap/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(150, 96, 125);\">Hyperspace Portal</a><span style=\"color: black;\">&nbsp;(a pre-requisite to get access to the Hyperspace MCP Registry).</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: black;\">3. Start&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: black;\">using&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"color: black;\">Claude Code!</span></p><p><br></p><p>4. Follow the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sap.sharepoint.com/:b:/r/teams/ClaudeCodeRollout/Shared%20Documents/General/Resources/20260310_Claude%20Code_Dos%26Donts.pdf?csf=1&amp;web=1&amp;e=5LhA55\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: rgb(243, 242, 241); color: blue;\"><strong><img src=\"//:0\" alt=\"​pdf icon\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\">&nbsp;Dos &amp; Don'ts</strong></a><strong style=\"color: black;\">&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"color: black;\">shared in the kick-off</span></p><p><span style=\"color: black;\">If you need help, please reach out to us via the&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/channel/19%3Afb167ed2fa604897908267d667ed0ff3%40thread.tacv2/Questions%20and%20Answers?groupId=f92ad6f5-67ec-4252-a77d-b41fef6bdf24&amp;tenantId=42f7676c-f455-423c-82f6-dc2d99791af7\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(150, 96, 125);\"><u>Claude Code Support channel</u></a><span style=\"color: black;\">.</span></p><p><br></p><p><strong style=\"color: black;\">Enjoy&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"color: black;\">AI-assisted coding with Claude Code!</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=86HM0RUWhCk</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Claude.md file</strong></p><p>https://www.skool.com/ai-automation-society/classroom/076a1c6e?md=5086a446f2bc47ccbc29988bad7cb5e4</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Design Inspiration:</strong></p><p>https://dribbble.com/search/landing%20page (dribble)</p><p>https://www.awwwards.com/directory/interactive/</p><p>https://21st.dev/community/components</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Vercel + Ai Studio</strong></p><p>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n0ahK4AheN4</p>"
    },
